{
  "stem": "17720.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 110.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was via train still, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] carrying the few meager luggages.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I only recall that in the very beginning, this was period in which I was seeing my mother only crying, very deeply depressed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because was a very big problem at the time to organize the foods, and the settling, resettling.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then came one radiance of the sun when my father came back still alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was unrecognizable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was almost not able to recognize him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was older maybe, with 50, 60 years older than what I knew him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He actually already had become like old man, with very thin, very-- with beards, white beard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When he left, he was-- had very beautiful black hair, strong black hair, he turned to an old man, almost unrecognizable.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This happiness that were existing and my family's cheerfulness, everything was completely lost, everything was killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was basically silence and sadness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Of course, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the spring was coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the nature don't care of what has happened with private human destiny, with all the beauty of new flowers, and romance.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[SIGHS] The young people, obviously that have the-- the-- very special quality to forget the bad thing, especially when they're very young, and trying to find the interesting and fascinating-- fascinating things in every new situation was what eventually vitalized my parents.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And obviously they had decided, or my mother decides obviously to have other child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But nevertheless, she become pregnant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And somewhere in the beginning of December, the new baby appear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was 19-- 1945.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before that, however, something else happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- obviously my activity didn't stop, or my love and interest for music didn't stop.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
